John Eunting, of Nottingham, senior, and Richard Halmark, of the same, complain of John Plumptre, of Nofflngham, of a plea of fraud and deceit. The same John de Plumptre was attached to answer to the aforesaid John Bunting and Richard Halmark of a plea of fraud and deceit.
